data.value: Its the morning of September 6th. Alex awakes from his slumber to get ready for his first day of school. He gets up and heads to the washroom to get freshened up before he gets dressed. Alex usually has his morning routine: 1) Brush Teeth 2) Wash Face 3) Comb hair 4) Style Hair. However, this morning he is feeling he needs to spice it up for his first day. How many ways can Alex spice up his morning routine?
